{"type": "article", "id": 60697, "title": "有位摄影师拍摄了一组照片，捕捉气球即将爆破的瞬间", "description": "感受一下既期待又焦虑的心情。", "date": "2019-01-27T22:46:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 56258, "name": "Daniel Forero"}, {"id": 267, "name": "平面设计"}, {"id": 42860, "name": "超现实"}], "category": 17, "author": 652712, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 107, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190127231222GgT6tbRC8USv9cOX.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">当你看别人吹气球，气球被越吹越大，感觉随时就要爆破时，是种什么心情？</p><p>是对即将发生的事情感到既期待又焦虑吗？</p><p>摄影艺术家 Daniel Forero&nbsp;想要唤起你的这种感觉。他拍摄了一组标题为“Air”的照片——想要捕捉气球即将爆破的瞬间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127223134ZUkPzWl6AVIrhae2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">照片中，没有人在吹气球，但是，充满气的气球被放置在厚重的大理石之间，看起来十分危险，已经处于爆破的边缘。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127223151UxYjAZB2aFcKv3Js.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.051314\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">并不清楚这些照片是怎么实现的，不过很有可能气球是 PS 的，也有可能，气球里装了水泥。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127223208btdOzIQB03roFgun.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.018450\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">不过 Daniel Forero 的作品总是充满超现实、荒诞的意味。<br></p><p class=\"\">比如“double skinned fruit（双层水果）”：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127223644t0hbEfWpBuRDJ9jC.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127223834cvtYPX6KnD1jTF79.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625263\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">尽管灵感是来自一句玩笑话。Forero 对一位朋友说：“瑞典太冷了，水果应该有双重皮肤。” 然后他想到，“我应该想象一下！”&nbsp;<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127223903IEmb8axHNtAhwS7d.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625263\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Forero 的另一个身份是艺术总监（自由职业），他曾在多家广告公司担任过平面设计师和艺术总监，作品屡次获奖，包括戛纳国际创意节 1 金 2 银 2 铜和纽约国际广告奖（New York Festivals）的银奖。<br></p><p class=\"\">合作过的客户包括 BMW、可口可乐、宝洁、飞利浦，联合利华、诺基亚等。<br></p><p>Forero 擅长让人们从他的创意作品中发现事物本身以外的含义。香烟的烟嘴变得很长很长，冰淇淋蛋筒长出仙人球，刷子的毛变成辫子，麦当劳的薯条变成了手指，香水里养了鱼......他将看似平常的日常事物重组或夸张化处理，告诉你“亲眼所见也许并非真实”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901272254355kpHDcdNVyFfw97l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700132\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127225627Nvpw4RaxLd8fOEjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700132\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127230234pTN1dBhA4G8HQXl2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700132\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127230251FnkWehOAKC4V9zRj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190127230309Sq57oPlcJGpjAtFZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700132\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901272303361CjhILaTzVxtyR29.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700132\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.daniel-forero.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Daniel Forero </a></p>"}